an_2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/travis">特拉维斯</a>在即将到来的英国巡演中与食品回馈捐赠平台合作，发起“Eat The Beat”活动。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="723" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/travis-share-single-gaslight-and-talk-new-album-l-a-times-america-is-so-wrapped-in-their-own-history-3604566"><b>特拉维斯分享单曲《Gaslight》并谈论新专辑《洛杉矶时报》：“美国如此沉浸在自己的历史中”</b></a></li></ul><p>乐队正在与 Bankuet 平台合作，为今年圣诞节使用食品银行的人们筹集资金，鼓励粉丝通过 Bankuet<a href="https://www.bankuet.co.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">网站</a>捐款，并在结帐时勾选“Eat The Beat”框。</p><p>粉丝们还有机会在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/travis-share-single-gaslight-and-talk-new-album-l-a-times-america-is-so-wrapped-in-their-own-history-3604566">12 月巡演</a>的每场演出中捐款，Bankuet 志愿者将在商品摊位工作。</p><p>主唱弗兰·希利 (Fran Healy) 表示：“我从小就很穷，所以我们与 Bankuet 联手，不仅帮助养活越来越多不得不依赖食品银行的人，还帮助那些面临取暖选择的低收入人群或者今年圣诞节吃东西。” </p><figure id="attachment_3815606" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3815606" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3815606" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Travis@2000x1270.jpg" alt="弗兰·希利（Fran Healy），特拉维斯乐队主唱" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Travis@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Travis@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Travis@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Travis@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Travis@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Travis@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3815606" class="wp-caption-text">弗兰·希利 (Fran Healy)，2024 年特拉维斯 (Travis) 主唱。图片来源：Pedro Becerra/Redferns/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> “寻求帮助并不丢脸，我每天都能得到免费的学校晚餐，这让我感到被关心，也许更重要的是，知道这帮助了我的妈妈，让我感觉更好，”他补充道。 “食物银行对于帮助英国有需要的家庭和个人解决餐桌上的食物至关重要。我们很幸运，我们有一些额外的钱可以买票去看演出，所以请投入几英镑或扔掉零钱或点击应用程序。”</p><p> Travis 的巡演将于 12 月 5 日在利兹 O2 Academy 拉开帷幕，整个月共演出 13 场。最后一晚是在格拉斯哥 OVO Hydro 举行的家乡演出。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/travis-share-delicate-new-single-bus-and-announce-2024-uk-tour-buy-tickets-3763542">在这里</a>找到完整的演出列表，并<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Ftravis-tickets%2Fartist%2F723651" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>找到任何剩余的门票。</p><p>明年 7 月 26 日，Travis 还将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-magic-numbers">The Magic Numbers</a>一起<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paul-heaton-travis-echo-the-bunnymen-faithless-halifax-summer-2025-headline-shows-3815599">在哈利法克斯的 Piece Hall 演出</a>。该演出是该场馆夏季系列演出的一部分， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-heaton">Paul Heaton</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/echo-and-the-bunnymen">Echo &amp; The Bunnymen</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/faithless">Faithless</a>也成为热门演出。</p><p>这支苏格兰乐队于七月发行了他们的第十张录音室专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/travis-share-single-gaslight-and-talk-new-album-l-a-times-america-is-so-wrapped-in-their-own-history-3604566">LA Times</a> 》，其中包括单曲《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/travis-share-single-gaslight-and-talk-new-album-l-a-times-america-is-so-wrapped-in-their-own-history-3604566">Gaslight</a> 》、《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/travis-share-delicate-new-single-bus-and-announce-2024-uk-tour-buy-tickets-3763542">Bus</a> 》和《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/travis-share-new-single-raze-the-bar-featuring-coldplays-chris-martin-and-the-killers-brandon-flowers-3754948">Raze The Bar</a> 》。这是他们八年来的第一张专辑，并且<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/travis-share-deluxe-version-of-l-a-times-featuring-10-extra-tracks-3799890">还在十月份推出了带有精简版的豪华版</a>。</p><p>专辑正式发行后不久，乐队透露<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/travis-used-the-beatles-lady-madonna-piano-to-record-single-gaslight-3775958">《煤气灯下》中使用的钢琴与披头士乐队《麦当娜夫人》中使用的钢琴相同</a>。</p><p>为了支持专辑的发行，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/travis-announce-exclusive-busking-set-in-london-3775891">乐队于7月在伦敦街头进行了街头表演</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/travis-surprise-fans-by-busking-in-glasgow-city-centre-on-a-vintage-double-decker-bus-3774801">此前还在格拉斯哥的一辆老式双层巴士上</a>进行了表演。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/travis-join-with-food-bank-donation-platform-to-launch-eat-the-beat-campaign-3816618">Travis 联合食品银行捐赠平台发起“Eat The Beat”活动的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
